mptom and the repeated reports of simulation instability.\n\nNo other untested or unreplaced component in the described system can periodically interrupt lamp current without a corresponding relay action or supply droop, both of which have been convincingly ruled out, making the switched‑cables indicator LED the remaining plausible root cause.'
